                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9431" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0311</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1333 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">造福桑梓，誉利兼行——娃哈哈ESG实践之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Benefit Society, Goodwill and Profit at the same time ——WaHaHa ESG Practice Tour</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张华，余祥丽，刘慧珍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州娃哈哈集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">娃哈哈；ESG；企业口碑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">WaHaHa; ESG; corporate reputation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国对生态文明建设的日益重视，以及“双碳”目标的明确提出，实施ESG战略对企业实现可持续发展具有重要意义。作为评估企业综合表现的非财务指标，ESG表现不仅成为了衡量其绩效和价值的重要尺度，更是一个向外界传递其内部实际生产经营信息的窗口。本案例选取杭州娃哈哈集团有限公司为实例，首先描述了娃哈哈从承担企业社会责任到实施ESG战略的背景，并解释了娃哈哈实施ESG战略的原因，接着详细梳理了娃哈哈在环境、社会和公司治理三方面的具体实践，随后表明了娃哈哈在“誉”和“利”等方面取得的收获，最后引发学生对于ESG助力娃哈哈实现可持续商业的思考。学生通过学习娃哈哈的ESG实践案例，可以更深入地理解ESG战略的内涵、驱动因素、具体行动策略以及实施成效。同时，这也有助于学生树立正确的商业价值观和伦理观，为未来的商业实践提供有益指导。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With China&#39;s increasing emphasis on ecological civilization construction and the explicit mention of the “dual-carbon” target, the implementation of ESG strategy is of great significance to enterprises in achieving sustainable development. As a non-financial indicator to assess the overall performance of an enterprise, ESG performance has not only become an important yardstick to measure its performance and value, but also a window to convey the actual internal production and operation information to the outside world. This case selects Hangzhou Wahaha Group Co., Ltd. as an example, firstly describes the background of Wahaha&#39;s transition from corporate social responsibility to the implementation of ESG strategy, and explains the reasons for Wahaha&#39;s implementation of the ESG strategy, and then combs through Wahaha&#39;s specific practices in the three aspects of environment, society and corporate governance in detail, and then shows Wahaha&#39;s performance in the areas of “reputation” and “profitability”, as well as the importance of ESG. It then shows the gains Wahaha has made in terms of “reputation” and “profit”, and finally triggers students to think about how ESG can help Wahaha realize sustainable business. By studying Wahaha&#39;s ESG practice case, students can gain a deeper understanding of the meaning, drivers, specific action strategies and implementation effectiveness of ESG strategy. At the same time, it also helps students to establish correct business values and ethics, providing useful guidance for future business practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG概念；ESG与企业社会责任的关系；利益相关者理论；信号传递理论；企业声誉及其形成机理；可持续发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
